{"tid":299214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跨國駭客組織「匿名者」：NASA將宣布發現外星人","createTime":"2017-06-27T01:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T07:23:03.000Z","uid":73262,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97501f363f6fe96162207bf6666632f653fae7b7","tid":299214,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:31:18.000Z","msg":"客組織「匿名者」（Anonymous）20日在網上發布影片，宣稱美國國家航空暨太空總署（NASA）即將宣布發現外星生命的證據。由於NASA近日才公布發現了10顆類地行星，還透露太空宜居帶的星球很多，也許人類並不孤單，讓NASA發現外星生物的傳聞不脛而走。<br />\n<br />\nYouTube頻道「全球匿名者」（Anonymous Global）20日上傳了一段長達12分鐘的影片，內容指出NASA科學任務理事會（SMD）總監澤布臣（Thomas Zurbuchen）近日在太空與科技委員會的會議上表示，「人類即將在宇宙中發現外星生命存在的證據」，且根據過去種種線索，人類已在發現外星生命的邊緣<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170626/953600.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170626%2F953600.htm&d=NN5D6p76vkHCv28B4St1m%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=378de95c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170626/953600.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7dce74182df0532123dc063892ec02fd66e284bf","tid":299214,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2846102b730fe503daa58ff2a962e634aa048e5","tid":299214,"uid":35941,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:33:43.000Z","msg":"好似年年都聽到呢d新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a059b6a01204d2ce7218067d5cf2a890cf68a05","tid":299214,"uid":59179,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"終於肯公布？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8182c54ca4cd61a6c16cb18825ff2e922b9a689","tid":299214,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T01:34:20.000Z","msg":"細菌"},{"pid":"d231c65e2